#

Beefy Stuffed Bell Peppers

$30
450 kcal

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

BeefComfort FoodFamily Meal

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with savory ground beef and rice, topped with cheese and baked to perfection.

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 6 lb
  • Bell peppers: 6 large
  • Cooked rice: 3 cups
  • Diced tomatoes: 2 cans (15 oz each)
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Cheddar cheese: 2 cups, shredded
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Paprika: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
